<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Paul Volcker</ENAMEX> in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1979</TIMEX>. Since <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Volcker</ENAMEX> was committed to taming inflation even at
