which meant that growth was lower and <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">entrepreneurs</ENAMEX> were worse off than
otherwise--for which we're paying the price <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">today</TIMEX>. The credit <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Reagan</ENAMEX> deserves
